district of Espoo, Finland **Kilo railway station, a commuter rail network in
Kilo, Espoo, Finland *KILO, a Colorado radio station *Kilo class submarine, the
NATO reporting name for a type of Russian submarine *Kilo Ali or Kilo, a rapper
from Atlanta, Georgia *Kilo or Kilo, a dance music artist/producer signed to
NextPlateau/Universal *Kilogram/Kilogramme a metric unit of mass *Men -
1 km Time Trial or Kilo, a cycling track time trial *Kilo, the letter K in
the ICAO spelling alphabet *El Kilo, an album by the Cuban hip hop group Orishas
**El Kilo (song), a song from the album El Kilo by Orishas *Kilo is a common
Arabic family name including: **Michel Kilo, Syrian Christian writer and human
rights activist **Wiz Kilo, a Syrian Canadian hip hop artist
